Prior to running the following commands, you need to install git and ansible
first.

Provision a vanilla Ubuntu 16.04 machine:
    ansible-playbook -i 'localhost,' -c local home-ubuntu.yml -K
    (Will be prompted for the sudo password. That is OK.)

Provision a vanilla MacOSX machine:
    ansible-playbook -i 'localhost,' -c local homembp.yml
